    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh i see. so basically the more i loop, the more memory it eats up because of those references. thanks. i'm actually trying to clean up some of these old test instances on my server though. if i run a termination command on a cluster, does it automatically clear all the linked child processes too, or could some of them stay running in the background?",
